{"tid":153233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴斯係香港/深圳做過縮唇手術？","createTime":"2017-03-12T12:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T14:26:06.000Z","uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea51ed8ae4fb78ef11355d03edb03f338c6ad04","tid":153233,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"小弟厚唇，想係箍完牙之後順便做縮唇整整佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問係香港同係深圳做既價錢有幾大差別？<br />\n有冇話有邊間醫院/邊個醫生好？<br />\n我自己google過d流程啊，術後康復啊果d，我諗應該都係大同小異，最緊要要搵個有經驗既醫生/醫院做到一個好既效果<br />\n唔知開係咩台好唯有直接開係吹水台<br />\n希望有做過既巴絲可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53030c3adebfb297373296fde7039877fbf0bf6b","tid":153233,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎嘴唇相嚟睇下先</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">想笑下</span></span>"},{"pid":"4d3f169812009c2a8040b7cf053a974a9b5a7486","tid":153233,"uid":28190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我驚你嘴唇都冇埋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54266dcc265f07aaff0e0174a4da82bcbfd3c3ad","tid":153233,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎嘴唇相嚟睇下先</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">想笑下</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132e09925a52ab9d737b051140743a22d3c32df1","tid":153233,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,